moticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   I like that idea of the classes who can cast a MR resist spell(aka me) on themselves again before they run back. I would have tried that myself if i wasn't so frantically excited about the whole thing at the time and it probably would have allowed me about 2 more seives.  Oh well on that, hehe.  I also wanted to say thanks for making the raid extremely fun for a first timer dragon raider.  Even tho we didn't win i didn't care, it was such great fun.  Makes me VERY happy i saw that shout in EC while playing my monk that the Vox raid was open to anyone <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .  Also let me have a chance to talk with some friends while i was there( aka Euwyn) and I agree that the cooperation was very good.  You guys do a heck of a dragon raid <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .  Thanks for everything guys!<br>
